longBusinessSummary: Bridgemarq Real Estate Services Inc. provides various services to residential real estate brokers and REALTORS in Canada. It offers information, tools, and services that assist its customers in the delivery of real estate services. The company provides its services under the Royal LePage, Via Capitale, and Johnston and Daniel brand names. The company was formerly known as Brookfield Real Estate Services Inc. and changed its name to Bridgemarq Real Estate Services Inc. in May 2019. Bridgemarq Real Estate Services Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
